<section class="content-section">
    <h2>Coming Soon</h2>
    <p>The BikeNode Web Extension is currently in development and will provide powerful shopping assistance tools for bike enthusiasts across multiple marketplaces and vendor websites.</p>
</section>

<section class="content-section">
    <h2>Planned Features</h2>
    <div class="feature-list">
        <div class="feature-item">
            <h3>Price Comparison</h3>
            <p>Automatically compare prices across multiple retailers for bikes, parts, and accessories to ensure you get the best deals.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-item">
            <h3>Marketplace Integration</h3>
            <p>Enhanced browsing experience on eBay, Craigslist, Facebook Marketplace, and other platforms with BikeNode data insights.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-item">
            <h3>Specification Lookup</h3>
            <p>Instant access to detailed bike specifications, reviews, and community insights while browsing listings or product pages.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-item">
            <h3>Community Reviews</h3>
            <p>See what the BikeNode community says about specific bikes, parts, and dealers right from their product pages.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-item">
            <h3>Saved Searches</h3>
            <p>Save and track searches across multiple platforms, get notifications when matching items are listed.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-item">
            <h3>Virtual Garage Integration</h3>
            <p>Easily add purchased items to your Virtual Garage, track compatibility with your existing bikes.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

